'''α-萘黄酮'''（又称'''7,8-苯并黄酮'''）是一种人工合成的<ref name=Campbell>{{cite journal | title = Flavonoid inhibition of aromatase enzyme activity in human preadipocytes | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-steroid-biochemistry-and-molecular-biology_1993-09_46_3/page/381 |author1=Campbell, Deborah R. |author2=Kurzer, Mindy S. | journal = Journal of Steroid Biochemistry and Molecular Biology | year = 1993 | volume = 46 | issue = 3 | pages = 381–388 | doi = 10.1016/0960-0760(93)90228-O | pmid = 9831487}}</ref><ref name=Kellis>{{cite journal |author1=Kellis JT Jr |author2=Vickery LE | title = Inhibition of human estrogen synthetase (aromatase) by flavones | journal = Science | year = 1984 | volume = 225 | issue = 4666 | pages = 1032–1034 | doi = 10.1126/science.6474163 | pmid = 6474163|bibcode=1984Sci...225.1032K }}</ref>[[黄酮类|黄酮类]]衍生物，可以由[[2-萘酚|2-萘酚]]和[[肉桂醛|肉桂醛]]制备而成。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1021/jo00312a023 | title = A new chromone and flavone synthesis and its utilization for the synthesis of potentially antitumorigenic polycyclic chromones and flavones | year = 1990 | last1 = Harvey | first1 = Ronald G. | last2 = Hahn | first2 = Jung Tai | last3 = Bukowska | first3 = Maria | last4 = Jackson | first4 = Henry | journal = The Journal of Organic Chemistry | volume = 55 | issue = 25 | pages = 6161}}</ref>

α-萘黄酮是一种强效的[[芳香化酶|芳香化酶]][[酶抑制剂|抑制剂]]，<ref name=Campbell/><ref name=Kellis/>实验发现其能导致幼鸡的睾丸发育出现异常。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Trefil, P. |author2=Micakova, A. |author3=Stiborova, M. |author4=Poplstein, M. |author5=Brillard, J.P. |author6=Hodek, P. | title =  Effects of alpha-naphthoflavone on body growth and gonad development in chickens (Gallus domesticus) | journal = Czech Journal of Animal Science - UZPI | year = 2004 | volume = 49 | issue = 6 | pages = 231–238|doi=10.17221/4305-CJAS}}</ref>

